</div>
<p class="gcf-txt-article">　</p>
<h2 class="gcf-ttl-h2"> <span class="gcf-ttl-h2__text">お礼の品をご紹介</span></h2>
</section>
<div id="products_list" class="gcf-lyt-detail__block2">
<ul class="goods_list">
</ul><ul class="goods_list">
<li class="goods-col">

<a target="_self" href="/product/detail/34545/180323/12">
<div class="goods-col_img">
<img src="https://img.furusato-tax.jp/img/x/product/details/20160722/pd_4f5b671219c8d3e1b8839f50c1097813e2d04042.jpg" alt="サンプル写真" class="goods-col_photo" decoding="async" />
</div>
<div class="goods-col_summary">
